I contributed the the problem now though that KEI lists for 120k and sells for 70-100k usually.  But what I don't understand is the silly bastards who cast it for free.  Sellers know that they can get 70-100K for it, and giving the best buff away for free just ensures that future enchanters will never recoup their money.<br>
<br>
I will admit that I am part of the problem, but giving buffs for free when plat is plentiful is just stupid and killing the enjoyment for the next tier of up and coming enchanters. (In this case).  I no longer cast the buff since most people will give me their 500 coppers and expect a grateful conversation, because of morons like you.  So I guess you are succeeding by driving c3 completely out of the game a a buff anyone would want to cast.<br>
<br>
Ainie 62 Enchanter Brell Serilis<br>
